frames.caption: An eagle and a goose stand facing each other in a lush, vibrant forest setting. A waterfall cascades in the background, surrounded by dense greenery and a clear blue sky with birds flying overhead.
frames.description: The scene depicts a serene and vibrant forest environment with an eagle and a goose as the central figures. The waterfall and lush greenery create a peaceful and natural backdrop.

frames.caption: A fantastical creature resembling a muscular bird with the body of a goose and the limbs of a powerful beast stands poised against a dramatic cloudy sky. Its wings are spread wide, showcasing a blend of feathers and sinewy muscles, while its talons grip the ground with intensity. The scene captures a moment of tension and strength, as if the creature is ready to take flight or engage in a powerful action.
frames.description: The scene depicts a surreal, mythical creature in a dramatic, stormy setting. The creature combines features of a bird and a beast, standing prominently with its wings extended against a backdrop of dark, swirling clouds.
